Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.41,0:00:03.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無限的時間將跳動停止
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.93,0:00:05.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人們悄聲無息地燃燒著
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.11,0:00:09.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有任何人注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.75,0:00:11.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界已經脫軌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.73,0:00:13.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被紅世之火所包圍
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,---------------------------OP-----------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.60,0:00:25.17,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}そして　この空　赤く染めて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.30,0:00:31.63,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}また来る時　この一身で　進むだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.08,0:00:48.24,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}すれ違っていく‘人’も　紛れ失くした‘モノ’も
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.24,0:00:53.19,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}いつかは　消えゆく記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.39,0:00:59.54,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}熱く揺るがす‘強さ’　儚く揺れる‘弱さ’
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.54,0:01:04.80,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}所詮　同じ結末
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.90,0:01:10.63,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}そんな日常　紅霞を溶かし
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.75,0:01:16.23,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}現れる陽　紅る世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.45,0:01:21.98,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}風になびかせ　線を引いて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.11,0:01:27.61,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}流れるような髪先　敵を刺す
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.78,0:01:33.31,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}振り斬った想い　漲る夢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.45,0:01:38.52,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}すべては今　この手で　使命
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.83,0:01:42.54,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,400)}果たしてゆくだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.60,0:00:25.17,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}於是這片天空被染成紅色
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.30,0:00:31.63,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}再度來臨之際  唯以此身不斷向前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.08,0:00:48.24,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}擦肩而過之「人」  紛亂迷失之「物」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.24,0:00:53.19,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}終將成為  消失的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.39,0:00:59.54,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}熱烈震撼的「堅強」  虛無飄渺的「脆弱」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.54,0:01:04.80,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}終究是  同一結局
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.90,0:01:10.63,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}如此平凡  溶化於晚霞之中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.75,0:01:16.23,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}升起的太陽  通紅的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.45,0:01:21.98,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}隨風飄揚  勾畫路線
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.11,0:01:27.61,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}宛如飄揚的髮梢  刺向敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.78,0:01:33.31,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}揮刀斬斷的思念  瀰漫夢境
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.45,0:01:42.54,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,400)}一切都於此刻  僅以這雙手達成使命
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,---------------------------ED-----------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.97,0:22:59.52,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}夜明け生まれ来るものよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.88,0:23:04.26,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}決して見失わないで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.73,0:23:09.12,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}You are you　少女よ　今こそ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.53,0:23:15.47,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}振りほどき立ちあがれ!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.28,0:23:36.33,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}胸の傷を隠したまま　風を切り進む君を
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.33,0:23:41.53,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}ただ見守る術など何もない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.27,0:23:50.38,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}その瞳はずっと先の　自分を探しているの?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.38,0:23:58.27,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}でも聞こえるよ　深い悲しみの鼓動が叫んでる!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.77,0:24:03.05,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I'm just　夜明け前の暗闇が
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.07,0:24:06.41,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}一生を運命づける
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.41,0:24:09.77,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}大丈夫　少女よ　今こそ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.77,0:24:15.37,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}悔やみ恥じることはない　Far way…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.37,0:24:22.97,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}十字を背負い　死ぬ気で炎を駆けろ!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.97,0:22:59.52,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}拂曉降生的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.88,0:23:04.26,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}決不可迷失自我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.73,0:23:09.12,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}You are you  少女啊  就是現在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.53,0:23:15.47,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}掙開手站起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.28,0:23:36.33,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}隱藏著胸口的傷痕  破風前進的你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.33,0:23:41.53,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}除了注視  我別無他法
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.27,0:23:50.38,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你那瞳孔是否正在  探尋著前方的自我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.38,0:23:58.27,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不過我能夠聽見  你那深情悲戚的心正在吶喊著
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.77,0:24:03.05,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I'm just  拂曉前的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.07,0:24:06.41,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}將此一生付為命運
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.41,0:24:09.77,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}沒事的  少女啊  就是現在
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.77,0:24:15.37,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}沒什麼好懊悔羞愧的  Far way…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.37,0:24:22.97,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}背負著十字架  以死的覺悟向著火焰疾走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.29,0:02:27.12,Optitle,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,0)\pos(315,240)}糾纏的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.64,0:01:48.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜和我在一起的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.84,0:01:52.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知何時開始像理所當然一樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.29,0:01:58.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也有時候夏娜看起來像個普通的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.71,0:02:00.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至會讓我忘記她是火霧戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.80,0:02:03.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.01,0:02:06.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和弗利安格內一戰以來的鍛煉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.52,0:02:12.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卻一口氣把我從這浮誇的心情里拉回了現實
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.19,0:02:15.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.35,0:02:19.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜是個強大又完美的火霧戰士這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.29,0:02:29.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,槽了槽了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.75,0:02:38.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好慢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.45,0:02:39.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.14,0:02:40.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.84,0:02:43.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和昨天一樣  感覺殺意躲避攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.34,0:02:45.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.33,0:02:51.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很合適啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.53,0:02:52.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.67,0:02:54.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.84,0:02:55.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要發呆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.39,0:02:57.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知  知道了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.39,0:03:06.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用那麼大力打也行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.36,0:03:09.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不適當的用點力是沒有意義的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.79,0:03:12.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不喜歡的話快點躲掉就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.91,0:03:15.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到現在還沒閉著眼睛鍛煉過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.34,0:03:16.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然這樣肯定不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.83,0:03:18.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果感覺殺意的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.37,0:03:20.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,單純的攻擊應該明白的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.20,0:03:24.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像知道對方要出什麼的猜拳一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.72,0:03:26.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.04,0:03:29.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說猜拳什麼的前一陣剛玩過
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.10,0:03:30.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還說得那麼了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.69,0:03:31.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果輸的一塌糊塗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.32,0:03:34.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了  吵死了  吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.23,0:03:37.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鍛煉中別說廢話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.11,0:03:40.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  等一下啊  搞突然襲擊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.78,0:03:42.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,攻擊總是很突然的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.54,0:03:43.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.06,0:03:44.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.10,0:03:49.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不像話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.01,0:03:53.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為說了廢話才會那麼丟臉的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.97,0:03:57.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都說了等下了  稍微等下也不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.42,0:03:59.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敵人可不會等的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.76,0:04:00.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說是這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.38,0:04:03.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這只是鍛煉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.22,0:04:05.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找藉口可很難看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.45,0:04:12.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,破了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.35,0:04:15.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是紅世之徒的話你已經被吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.02,0:04:17.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.85,0:04:18.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天就到這吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.44,0:04:20.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要準備去學校了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.38,0:04:22.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.65,0:04:25.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  小悠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.56,0:04:27.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經結束了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.25,0:04:29.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二自作主張結束的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.51,0:04:32.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為鍛煉進行得不太順利
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.37,0:04:36.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的呢  好像給打得很慘
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.67,0:04:38.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前更加不像樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.51,0:04:41.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但卻擺出一副悠然自得的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.45,0:04:45.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或許察覺到自己比較差勁了也說不定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.09,0:04:47.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差勁？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.50,0:04:50.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夏娜是那麼可愛又小巧玲瓏的女孩子呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.41,0:04:55.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被打的四腳朝天  作為男孩子來說總有些丟臉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.45,0:04:58.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我比較強  這也沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.14,0:05:01.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是呢  男孩子都是愛面子的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.28,0:05:04.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特別是在想讓她看到優點的女孩子面前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.40,0:05:10.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我經常想著悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.78,0:05:13.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是對悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.30,0:05:19.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一路小心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.86,0:05:30.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天放學以後
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.28,0:05:31.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,張開封絕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.74,0:05:33.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微做些動作幅度大的鍛煉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.86,0:05:35.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.07,0:05:40.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然做這麼誇張的事沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.77,0:05:43.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是為了沒問題才鍛煉的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.32,0:05:46.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說是這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.69,0:05:50.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為男孩子來說總有些丟臉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.37,0:05:54.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要鍛煉的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.17,0:05:55.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到時候就不丟臉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.23,0:05:58.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這  算是在鼓勵我？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.62,0:06:01.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是說理所當然的話而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.35,0:06:04.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說現在相當丟臉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.10,0:06:33.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丟臉什麼的  這種無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.26,0:06:38.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重要的是  悠二能變強然後一起戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.78,0:06:39.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永遠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.98,0:06:41.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  有一元硬幣的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.08,0:06:49.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去小賣部吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.70,0:06:50.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.10,0:06:52.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大姐的情況怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.64,0:06:53.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是老樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.50,0:06:56.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉  不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.55,0:06:59.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但大姐恢復原樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.39,0:07:00.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就會離開這個城市了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.55,0:07:02.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.89,0:07:07.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我是希望大姐恢復原樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.73,0:07:08.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.55,0:07:10.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道啦知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.03,0:07:12.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.27,0:07:15.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,緒方同學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.38,0:07:17.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.04,0:07:19.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.88,0:07:25.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇…！這是一美做的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.06,0:07:26.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.63,0:07:27.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是吉田同學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.00,0:07:31.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朋友給了我料理的配方  就想試試看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.47,0:07:32.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.16,0:07:35.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個  請
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.69,0:07:36.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不喜歡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.69,0:07:37.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.13,0:07:38.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.20,0:07:45.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小緣喜歡的話也
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.28,0:07:47.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.94,0:07:49.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好味
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.36,0:07:52.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這和外面賣的完全不一樣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.78,0:07:53.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.20,0:07:55.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.23,0:07:57.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉田同學料理很拿手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.81,0:08:02.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  只是愛好而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.62,0:08:09.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然  好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.27,0:08:11.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但不好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.21,0:08:14.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打擾了  圖書管理員在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.18,0:08:17.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  我和她
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.66,0:08:19.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有空嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.10,0:08:22.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說是圖書館的書今天要變更排放順序了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.41,0:08:25.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放學後在圖書館集合
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.33,0:08:26.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.98,0:08:28.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為每個班級要派兩人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.45,0:08:29.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果沒空的話找個代替的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.53,0:08:31.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.95,0:08:32.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.20,0:08:36.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  要去探望外婆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.67,0:08:38.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一家人都
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.32,0:08:40.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.44,0:08:44.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那坂井  你和吉田同學一起去好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.75,0:08:46.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要上補習班
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.28,0:08:48.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有空吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.35,0:08:50.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.35,0:08:51.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.75,0:08:52.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉田同學  可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.43,0:08:55.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  不添麻煩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.33,0:08:57.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正規定兩個人了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.76,0:08:59.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.52,0:09:01.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝  幫大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.51,0:09:03.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.85,0:09:05.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.53,0:09:11.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天放學以後
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.94,0:09:12.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,張開封絕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.33,0:09:15.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微做些動作幅度大的鍛煉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.55,0:09:17.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.57,0:09:18.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和別人說好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.55,0:09:22.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  說過要借平井同學的筆記看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.37,0:09:26.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平井同學  下次好了  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.32,0:09:35.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.23,0:09:37.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為是我提出的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.71,0:09:39.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.56,0:09:50.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.27,0:09:50.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.19,0:09:54.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但因為是學校的委員會
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.83,0:09:56.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上再鍛煉也行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.12,0:09:59.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說過今天放學後做的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.66,0:10:01.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.55,0:10:02.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拒絕就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.90,0:10:04.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都已經答應了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.29,0:10:05.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事到如今可說不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.79,0:10:07.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鍛煉才比較重要吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.27,0:10:10.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個  但學校也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.76,0:10:12.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種根本無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.71,0:10:13.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且是我先提出的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.64,0:10:16.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才道歉了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.51,0:10:19.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說要鍛煉的不是悠二嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.09,0:10:21.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話是這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.68,0:10:22.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就今天一天有什麼關係
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.30,0:10:25.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二太沒決心了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.85,0:10:27.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.28,0:10:29.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之今天就是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.05,0:10:30.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.66,0:10:36.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.78,0:10:38.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪有這麼任性的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.04,0:10:40.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要參加委員會
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.21,0:10:44.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二不鍛煉不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.11,0:10:47.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為非常弱  非常丟臉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.96,0:10:51.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像現在這樣完全派不上用處
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.90,0:10:53.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.22,0:10:55.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種事我明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.42,0:10:58.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.45,0:11:04.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平井同學怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.64,0:11:06.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  完全沒有生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.99,0:11:09.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說只是出去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.49,0:11:11.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.73,0:11:14.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉田同學  今天要和坂井一起加班了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.77,0:11:15.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.55,0:11:35.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  小夏娜一個人？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.39,0:11:36.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小悠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.69,0:11:38.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天參加了委員會什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.80,0:11:42.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎  那在裡面等如何
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.96,0:11:44.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做了好吃的布丁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.14,0:11:51.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夏娜原來是一個人住啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.10,0:11:52.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真辛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.39,0:11:54.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼  已經習慣了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.04,0:11:59.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃  千草的也很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.65,0:12:01.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.87,0:12:02.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說  小夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.22,0:12:04.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這吃晚餐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.03,0:12:18.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.49,0:12:22.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦  回去的時候和坂井獨處
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.29,0:12:25.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說什麼好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.00,0:12:28.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萬一沒話題了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.06,0:12:30.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.19,0:12:31.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.47,0:12:34.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  剛才聽說了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.57,0:12:37.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,2班的平井同學測驗全是100分
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.43,0:12:39.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.68,0:12:41.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像體育課上也很厲害哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.20,0:12:43.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還真有呢  那樣的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.49,0:12:50.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那  那個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.49,0:12:55.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  那個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.20,0:13:00.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想問  關於小緣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.83,0:13:02.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣總是一個人想下去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.21,0:13:03.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.56,0:13:08.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是怎麼看待小緣的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.79,0:13:10.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.90,0:13:15.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然剛才3班的人也說過了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.26,0:13:17.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很厲害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.76,0:13:20.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  真是厲害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.88,0:13:24.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  夏娜太厲害了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.03,0:13:27.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋笨蛋  真是太沒膽子了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.57,0:13:33.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.46,0:13:36.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小悠真慢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.41,0:13:40.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夏娜都已經吃好飯洗完澡了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.43,0:13:42.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.83,0:13:43.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖是我以前的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.01,0:13:45.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但小夏娜說我想穿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.83,0:13:48.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  嗯  挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.00,0:13:49.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小悠
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.73,0:13:51.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很晚了就送她回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.69,0:13:58.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果知道夏娜晚上住我房間的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.97,0:14:00.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,母親會嚇一跳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.93,0:14:04.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.15,0:14:11.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天份的鍛煉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.34,0:14:15.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了  反正已經很晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.76,0:14:17.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.96,0:14:18.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.88,0:14:23.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.75,0:14:28.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙始終也只是個無聊的凡人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.62,0:14:32.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紅世之徒  對  只要來了就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.48,0:14:34.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是火霧戰士也無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.90,0:14:37.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要戰鬥的話  就算是悠二也
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.51,0:14:58.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.96,0:15:01.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.04,0:15:05.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,存在之力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.71,0:15:08.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的存在之力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.81,0:15:15.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.65,0:15:16.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,磷子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.59,0:15:18.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.99,0:15:23.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這封絕還真爛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.06,0:15:24.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.65,0:15:27.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是不去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.79,0:15:29.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒心情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.57,0:15:32.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？身為悼詞朗誦者你不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.67,0:15:35.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但就是這樣了也沒辦法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.56,0:15:38.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一句話也說不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.75,0:15:39.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,低谷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.28,0:15:47.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正好  就交給小鬼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.16,0:15:49.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.12,0:15:54.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二沒有來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.71,0:15:55.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二沒有來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.47,0:15:57.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.77,0:15:59.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是要悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.20,0:16:10.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.16,0:16:15.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的  我的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.94,0:16:16.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像錯亂了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.24,0:16:20.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕是失去主人的磷子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.51,0:16:21.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失去了主人？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.36,0:16:23.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就算放著不管
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.04,0:16:24.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒幾天也會消失的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.96,0:16:25.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.68,0:16:28.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為磷子不管吞食了多少存在之力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.55,0:16:30.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都不能變成自己的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.81,0:16:32.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火霧戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.67,0:16:35.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,殺了主人的混蛋討伐工具
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.55,0:16:37.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我可不會被消滅的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.21,0:16:38.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會消失的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.48,0:16:40.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  你會消失
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.89,0:16:43.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要  我要存在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.82,0:16:57.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的  我的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.80,0:16:58.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.53,0:17:01.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙的身體軟撲撲的真難砍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.83,0:17:11.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要消除我的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.15,0:17:14.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要砍  不要砍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.23,0:17:20.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有預定要出門嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.88,0:17:25.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為從剛才開始就坐立不安的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.46,0:17:26.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老是看外面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.84,0:17:30.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和朋友說過
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.65,0:17:32.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但不去也沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.56,0:17:34.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.99,0:17:36.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為去也派不上用場的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.08,0:17:38.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被這麼說了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.11,0:17:40.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是你自己說的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.86,0:17:43.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.66,0:17:49.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,存在  存在之力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.05,0:17:50.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放棄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.42,0:17:52.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎麼吃你都會消失
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.60,0:17:54.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會消失
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.25,0:17:56.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會消失
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.48,0:17:57.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.76,0:17:58.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算那麼巨大
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.28,0:18:01.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本體的核心卻是很小的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.42,0:18:04.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在毀掉之前只有不斷砍了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.43,0:18:12.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的存在還沒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.82,0:18:15.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不吃的話  存在之力就
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.39,0:18:17.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都說沒用的了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.21,0:18:21.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛  好痛  好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.36,0:18:24.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.73,0:18:26.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要消滅我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.39,0:18:28.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要消除我的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.64,0:18:30.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了  吵死了  吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.05,0:18:32.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我吃飽了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.68,0:18:34.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說小悠
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.59,0:18:36.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.44,0:18:40.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是為了讓小悠派上用場而教你的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.27,0:18:46.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想只是陪在那個人身邊也能幫上忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.19,0:18:49.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我吃飽了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.89,0:18:51.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照顧不周
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.97,0:19:08.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想只是陪在那個人身邊也能幫上忙的
