Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.75,0:20:53.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,變得更強
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.93,0:20:58.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會的  會變強的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.09,0:21:02.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了能讓我們在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.08,0:21:09.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真髒啊  別把垃圾亂丟
