Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.87,0:21:15.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有錢人家的闊少爺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.12,0:21:18.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  說說看Help  me什麼的
