Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.96,0:21:48.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還沒吃掉這些傢伙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.23,0:21:50.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥可真是的
