Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.03,0:21:57.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以了喲  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.05,0:22:00.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請別客氣儘管吃吧
